==Getting there==
[[File:Smoke Dungeon dust devils.png|thumb|left|The dust devil area.]]
*Using a [[Nardah teleport|Nardah Teleport]] and then taking a magic carpet to Pollnivneach
*Using Desert Amulet and then taking a magic carpet to Pollnivneach
*Home teleport (if house is in Pollnivneach)
*Home teleport tabs and a scroll of redirection
*Teleport to Al Kharid (amulet of glory, ring of dueling, etc.), go through the Shantay Pass, and take a magic carpet to Pollnivneach

